Combine baby spinach, baby arugula, blueberries, and onion in a large bowl. Add the Double Blue Dressing (see below). Toss to combine. Sprinkle with pecans and the 1/4 cup blue cheese. Whisk together the VOSKOS(R) Nonfat Blueberry Greek Yogurt, balsamic vinegar, and olive oil in a bowl. Stir in the 2 tablespoons blue cheese. Cover and chill until serving time.